  44:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Normal transfers (legacy)
  45:../STM32Cube_FW_N6/Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Linked-list transfers
